OL,3,CJeremy Hunt's latest economic
OL,4,Cdecisions show how boxed in he is
OL,6,FWhen I saw tonight's FT headline that
OL,7,Fthe chancellor is considering the
OL,8,Fabolition of thein next week's budget
OL,9,FI thought it must be an early April
OL,10,Ffool.
OL,12,FBut it is true.
OL,14,FSo concerned is Jeremy Hunt that he
OL,15,Fwon't have enough in the kitty for a
OL,16,Fsizeable cut in personal income taxes
OL,17,F- a giveaway more-or-less promised by
OL,18,Fthe PM - that he is considering even
OL,19,Fthat capitulation.
