OL,3,CJeremy Hunt's latest economic
OL,4,Cdecisions show how boxed in he is
OL,6,FThe UK's so-called non-dom status
OL,7,Fallows foreign nationals to live and
OL,8,Fwork in the UK for 15 years free of
OL,9,Fthe requirement to pay UK tax on their
OL,10,Fearnings on capital held abroad.
OL,12,FThe prime minister's heiress wife
OL,13,FAkshata is (although she latterly
OL,14,Fvolunteered to pay UK tax on her
OL,15,Fglobal income).
OL,17,FLabour has pledged to abolish the tax
OL,18,Fbreak for wealthy non-nationals.
