OL,3,CJeremy Hunt's latest economic
OL,4,Cdecisions show how boxed in he is
OL,6,FOne counter-intuitive problem for
OL,7,FJeremy Hunt is that inflation is lower
OL,8,Fthan the official forecaster the OBR
OL,9,Fthought it would be in the autumn,
OL,10,Fsuch that "fiscal drag" - the refusal
OL,11,Fto up-rate tax thresholds in line with
OL,12,Finflation - raises less money than
OL,13,Fexpected.
OL,15,FOn the contrary, the yield on 10-year
OL,16,Fgilts - another name for the interest
OL,17,Frate paid by the government when
OL,18,Fborrowing - has risen sharply in the
OL,19,Flast month.
