OL,3,CJeremy Hunt's latest economic
OL,4,Cdecisions show how boxed in he is
OL,6,FSo the OBR is forecasting that the
OL,7,Fgovernment's interest payments will be
OL,8,Fhigher than it expected.JThe net
OL,9,Feffect is that there is less
OL,10,F"headroom" in the OBR's five-year debt
OL,11,Fprojection for tax cuts, or almost no
OL,12,Fheadroom at all.
OL,14,FHence the to contemplate abolishing
OL,15,Fnon-dom status. There is also raw
OL,16,Fpolitics here.
